  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help 16 girls to go on an annual educational tour</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project builds resilience among 16 marginalized adolescent girls (10-18) in South India, providing them with rich and vibrant experience of going on an educational tour for 4 days  to places of historical &amp; educational importance.  We plan to travel by air to New Delhi in January, 2019 and return by train .   These annual out of state tours exposes the girls to different cultures, languages and foods where they learn to embrace diversity &amp; tolerance which forms the foundation of resilience.</narrative>
  </description>
